{"id": 2488, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心x贝壳租房】在试图解决“住不好”时，你pick了哪些操作？", "description": "你总有一招我不知道（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 7714, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201807301218144mSDHB6FnXMUeqdG.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-07-29T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 296458, "content": "有床就能放弃了一切。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1424219}, {"id": 296720, "content": "天黑走在回去的路上，一点开手机里的音乐，推荐歌单里正中下怀的民谣在耳机里响起起，突然鼻子一酸，嘴角不自觉上扬……然后继续用高傲自信的姿态向前，眼里却只有，隐约的，回家的方向。偶尔被天上唯一的一颗星星吸引，以及忽暗忽亮的路灯。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1395007}, {"id": 295956, "content": "一个室友只能开黑了，两个室友可以斗地主了，三个室友凑一桌就是麻将", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1422126}, {"id": 295705, "content": "立即具有“工匠精神”，别说修理了，我就是鲁班本人！", "image": null, "praise_count": 312, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 295706, "content": "同事纷纷下班，我却假装加班迟迟不回；那个所谓的房子不过是个睡觉的地方。", "image": null, "praise_count": 478, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 295707, "content": "更加努力奋斗，争取提薪升职，让未来的自己住的更好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 264, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 295708, "content": "（咣咣凿门声）“X先生，快递” “放门口就行” 一个人住，女生装男生是必备技能。", "image": null, "praise_count": 364, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 296503, "content": "一旦沦为房贷狗 工作都认真起来了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1157735}, {"id": 295740, "content": "听到隔壁巨大的噪音，我也只能与对方互敲暖气作为回应了", "image": null, "praise_count": 120, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1143922}, {"id": 295741, "content": "悄咪咪的安装摄像头，让我看看是谁帮（偷）我（吃）减（零）肥（食）", "image": null, "praise_count": 208, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1420908}, {"id": 295742, "content": "点一根线香开始安慰自己“佛说要忍耐”", "image": null, "praise_count": 555, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1173153}, {"id": 295743, "content": "每日通勤的距离等于一本书的时间，我也是饱览群书的说。", "image": null, "praise_count": 313, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 505814}, {"id": 295745, "content": "买自己喜欢的小物装点", "image": null, "praise_count": 119, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1405424}, {"id": 295746, "content": "一趟在床上就听到楼上小朋友撒欢似的跑步声！10点半了还不睡！明天要去幼儿园的好伐", "image": null, "praise_count": 169, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1168185}, {"id": 295747, "content": "下次花多点钱住更好的", "image": null, "praise_count": 217, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1230166}, {"id": 295748, "content": "有一张床一个空调就好了 没有过住不好的问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 132, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950816}, {"id": 295751, "content": "有钱就不存在住不好的问题啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 136, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1207126}, {"id": 295752, "content": "能不回去就尽量在外面浪咯～～", "image": null, "praise_count": 248, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1328299}, {"id": 295754, "content": "养一只主子消磨自己的钱包耗费自己的时间，就没有精力去care其他的事啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 244, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107204}, {"id": 295755, "content": "闭上眼睛开始回味刚刚的晚餐~吃比睡重要", "image": null, "praise_count": 177, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107203}, {"id": 295757, "content": "每天面对房子，暗下决心好好工作努力赚钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 402, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208858}, {"id": 295760, "content": "戴上耳机找个好电影，你闹你的，我看我的", "image": null, "praise_count": 149, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1212038}, {"id": 295763, "content": "回去躺着追剧呀，游戏呀，累了就洗洗睡，闹钟响了起床上班呀", "image": null, "praise_count": 101, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378847}, {"id": 295765, "content": "能动手对地方确实不多。", "image": null, "praise_count": 162, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1420943}, {"id": 295766, "content": "不毕业\n住学校", "image": "img/option/option/201807301504252Y5h46bPLkayAi1W", "praise_count": 243, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1362634}, {"id": 295769, "content": "还未遇到过，可能我心态太好了。?", "image": null, "praise_count": 167, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1420987}, {"id": 295770, "content": "种点花养点草，嗯，挺好！", "image": null, "praise_count": 146, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1356376}, {"id": 296026, "content": "看大家聊了那么多\n感觉离开家\n自己出来租房\n需要更大的勇气", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 602753}, {"id": 295773, "content": "科室七个人，三个领导、两个怀孕、一个准备结婚、还有一个我干着所有的活", "image": null, "praise_count": 121, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1420875}, {"id": 295775, "content": "花心思收拾", "image": null, "praise_count": 132, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1421021}, {"id": 295777, "content": "找一个好人一起住", "image": null, "praise_count": 152, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1421036}, {"id": 295779, "content": "新来的合租女室友天天防贼一样防着我们～", "image": null, "praise_count": 163, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711174}, {"id": 295780, "content": "有条件的就换，没有条件的也只能忍", "image": null, "praise_count": 218, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1225142}, {"id": 296548, "content": "和人合租", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1405424}, {"id": 296549, "content": "住远一点 住好一点", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1405424}, {"id": 296550, "content": "搬家", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1235379}, {"id": 295783, "content": "搬家……", "image": null, "praise_count": 133, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 620900}, {"id": 296551, "content": "努力加班 努力赚钱 换一个好点的房子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1424868}, {"id": 295784, "content": "加班，加班，加班，加到开心", "image": null, "praise_count": 152, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1223792}, {"id": 296561, "content": "安静的看着天花板", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1344200}, {"id": 295795, "content": "和邻居互敲墙导致双方墙皮掉了好几层，年底大概能当上同居室友了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 328, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1420426}, {"id": 295796, "content": "每一次搬来搬去，都是我断舍离的修炼大法～", "image": null, "praise_count": 182, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1421114}, {"id": 295800, "content": "就算花掉所有积蓄，也要换房子", "image": null, "praise_count": 85, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1406959}, {"id": 295801, "content": "我最近膨胀了，连买房子这种也敢点进来看了", "image": null, "praise_count": 106, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1384226}, {"id": 296569, "content": "晚上睡得好，白天才有干劲。可是！睡觉认枕头这事真的好烦躁！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1424920}, {"id": 295802, "content": "养个猫能解决一切吃住问题，除了行…… ", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181495}, {"id": 296066, "content": "听到奇怪的声音会砸墙", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340726}, {"id": 295812, "content": "通过两个卧室相通的结构，把一个空调变成两个房间的共用空调??", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1310834}, {"id": 295814, "content": "只要地面干净，什么条件都可以", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1421177}, {"id": 296582, "content": "外面那么美好，为什么不在外面浪呢～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208858}]}